From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Mon, 16 Feb 2026 14:28:47 -0600
Subject: [PATCH 12/42] Accept pixel dims and resize on the fly
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

The server sat content at default size,
A hidden window, small and unwise.
Now XPC sends the pixels true,
And resize makes the viewport new—
Each frame arrives at perfect guise.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
